{"tha-ap549:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap549:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap549:0.3":"Abhayattheraapadana ","tha-ap549:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap549:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","tha-ap549:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap549:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap549:2.1":"Saranagamane kinci, ","tha-ap549:2.2":"nivesesi tathagato; ","tha-ap549:2.3":"Kinci sile nivesesi, ","tha-ap549:2.4":"dasakammapathuttame. ","tha-ap549:3.1":"Deti kassaci so viro, ","tha-ap549:3.2":"samannaphalamuttamam; ","tha-ap549:3.3":"Samapatti tatha attha, ","tha-ap549:3.4":"tisso vijja pavecchati. ","tha-ap549:4.1":"Chalabhinnasu yojesi, ","tha-ap549:4.2":"kinci sattam naruttamo; ","tha-ap549:4.3":"Deti kassaci natho so, ","tha-ap549:4.4":"catasso patisambhida. ","tha-ap549:5.1":"Bodhaneyyam pajam disva, ","tha-ap549:5.2":"asankheyyampi yojanam; ","tha-ap549:5.3":"Khanena upagantvana, ","tha-ap549:5.4":"vineti narasarathi. ","tha-ap549:6.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap549:6.2":"ahosim brahmanatrajo; ","tha-ap549:6.3":"Paragu sabbavedanam, ","tha-ap549:6.4":"veyyakaranasammato. ","tha-ap549:7.1":"Niruttiya ca kusalo, ","tha-ap549:7.2":"nighandumhi visarado; ","tha-ap549:7.3":"Padako ketubhavidu, ","tha-ap549:7.4":"chandovicitikovido. ","tha-ap549:8.1":"Janghaviharam vicaram, ","tha-ap549:8.2":"hamsaramamupeccaham; ","tha-ap549:8.3":"Addasam varadam settham, ","tha-ap549:8.4":"mahajanapurakkhatam. ","tha-ap549:9.1":"Desentam virajam dhammam, ","tha-ap549:9.2":"paccanikamati aham; ","tha-ap549:9.3":"Upetva tassa kalyanam, ","tha-ap549:9.4":"sutvana vimalam aham. ","tha-ap549:10.1":"Byahatam punaruttam va, ","tha-ap549:10.2":"apattham va niratthakam; ","tha-ap549:10.3":"Naddasam tassa munino, ","tha-ap549:10.4":"tato pabbajito aham. ","tha-ap549:11.1":"Nacireneva kalena, ","tha-ap549:11.2":"sabbasattavisarado; ","tha-ap549:11.3":"Nipuno buddhavacane, ","tha-ap549:11.4":"ahosim gunisammato. ","tha-ap549:12.1":"Tada catasso gathayo, ","tha-ap549:12.2":"ganthayitva subyanjana; ","tha-ap549:12.3":"Santhavitva tilokaggam, ","tha-ap549:12.4":"desayissam dine dine. ","tha-ap549:13.1":"‘Virattosi mahaviro, ","tha-ap549:13.2":"samsare sabhaye vasam; ","tha-ap549:13.3":"Karunaya na nibbayi, ","tha-ap549:13.4":"tato karuniko muni. ","tha-ap549:14.1":"Puthujjano vayo santo, ","tha-ap549:14.2":"na kilesavaso ahu; ","tha-ap549:14.3":"Sampajano satiyutto, ","tha-ap549:14.4":"tasma eso acintiyo. ","tha-ap549:15.1":"Dubbalani kilesani, ","tha-ap549:15.2":"yassasayagatani me; ","tha-ap549:15.3":"Nanaggiparidaddhani, ","tha-ap549:15.4":"na khiyimsu tamabbhutam. ","tha-ap549:16.1":"Yo sabbalokassa garu, ","tha-ap549:16.2":"loko yassa tatha garu; ","tha-ap549:16.3":"Tathapi lokacariyo, ","tha-ap549:16.4":"loko tassanuvattako’. ","tha-ap549:17.1":"Evamadihi sambuddham, ","tha-ap549:17.2":"kittayam dhammadesanam; ","tha-ap549:17.3":"Yavajivam karitvana, ","tha-ap549:17.4":"gato saggam tato cuto. ","tha-ap549:18.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap549:18.2":"yam buddhamabhikittayim; ","tha-ap549:18.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap549:18.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap549:19.1":"Devaloke maharajjam, ","tha-ap549:19.2":"padesim kancanagghiyam; ","tha-ap549:19.3":"Cakkavatti maharajjam, ","tha-ap549:19.4":"bahusonubhavim aham. ","tha-ap549:20.1":"Duve bhave pajayami, ","tha-ap549:20.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap549:20.3":"Annam gatim na janami, ","tha-ap549:20.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap549:21.1":"Duve kule pajayami, ","tha-ap549:21.2":"khattiye atha brahmane; ","tha-ap549:21.3":"Nice kule na jayami, ","tha-ap549:21.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap549:22.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap549:22.2":"giribbajapuruttame; ","tha-ap549:22.3":"Rannoham bimbisarassa, ","tha-ap549:22.4":"putto namena cabhayo. ","tha-ap549:23.1":"Papamittavasam gantva, ","tha-ap549:23.2":"niganthena vimohito; ","tha-ap549:23.3":"Pesito nataputtena, ","tha-ap549:23.4":"buddhasetthamupeccaham. ","tha-ap549:24.1":"Pucchitva nipunam panham, ","tha-ap549:24.2":"sutva byakaranuttamam; ","tha-ap549:24.3":"Pabbajitvana naciram, ","tha-ap549:24.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap549:25.1":"Kittayitva jinavaram, ","tha-ap549:25.2":"kittito homi sabbada; ","tha-ap549:25.3":"Sugandhadehavadano, ","tha-ap549:25.4":"asim sukhasamappito. ","tha-ap549:26.1":"Tikkhahasalahupanno, ","tha-ap549:26.2":"mahapanno tathevaham; ","tha-ap549:26.3":"Vicittapatibhano ca, ","tha-ap549:26.4":"tassa kammassa vahasa. ","tha-ap549:27.1":"Abhitthavitva padumuttaraham, ","tha-ap549:27.2":"Pasannacitto asamam sayambhum; ","tha-ap549:27.3":"Na gacchi kappani apayabhumim, ","tha-ap549:27.4":"Satamsahassani balena tassa. ","tha-ap549:28.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap549:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap549:28.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap549:29.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap549:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap549:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap549:30.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap549:30.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap549:30.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap549:31.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma abhayo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap549:32.1":"Abhayattherassapadanam sattamam. "}